<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<div class="about-container">
    
    <h1>About N3W5</h1>

    <h2>Welcome to N3W5</h2>

    <p>Founded in 2024 by Laszlo and David, N3W5 is a dynamic online platform designed to provide valuable insights and access to global news content. Our mission is to empower news organizations, newspapers, and news channels with a powerful research tool that aggregates content from various sources, including Google News and other APIs.</p>

    <h3>Our Vision</h3>

    <p>In a rapidly evolving digital landscape, staying informed is crucial. N3W5 aims to be a catalyst for information exchange, offering a centralized hub where news professionals can seamlessly access and explore news articles from around the world.</p>

    <h3>The Team Behind N3W5</h3>

    <p>N3W5 is the brainchild of Laszlo and David, passionate individuals with a shared vision for enhancing the way news is consumed and analyzed. Their combined expertise in technology and information processing has driven the development of this innovative platform.</p>

    <h3>Key Features</h3>

    <p><strong>1. Aggregated Content</strong></p>

    <p>N3W5 brings together content from Google News and other APIs, ensuring a comprehensive overview of global news at your fingertips.</p>

    <p><strong>2. Translation Tool</strong></p>

    <p>Breaking down language barriers, our integrated translation tool allows you to read articles in your preferred language, facilitating seamless research and analysis.</p>

    <h3>Legal</h3>
    
    <p>All articles are collected from News APIs solely for the purpose of providing information to our users. We respect copyright laws and endeavor to use content in accordance with Fair Use principles. If there are any copyright issues that don't fall under Fair Use, or if you believe your rights have been infringed, please contact us at n3w5@service.com with details of your concern. We will promptly investigate and take appropriate action, which may include removing the content or providing proper attribution. Your feedback is valuable to us as we strive to ensure the integrity of our content and operations.</p>
    
    <h3>Intended Use</h3>

    <p>Designed specifically for newspapers and news channels, N3W5 is an invaluable resource for researchers, journalists, and news professionals. Please note that the posts generated on our platform should not be made public due to potential copyright considerations.</p>

    <h3>Join Us in Shaping the Future of News</h3>

    <p>N3W5 invites news organizations to join us in our mission to revolutionize the way news is discovered, consumed, and analyzed. Together, let's embark on a journey of information excellence.</p>

    <p>For inquiries, collaborations, or to access N3W5, please contact us at: n3w5@service.com.</p>

    <p>Thank you for choosing N3W5 as your trusted news research companion.</p>
    
